author: Tim Trinkle
comment: Wow. So simple! While initially mocked, I think you'll find that "Yo!-ing" is a much more efficient way of asking someone whats going on. I truly enjoy this app. While this is the case, due to the initial mocking reviews that were written, I am having difficulty getting friends to sign up. Please add the functionality to send "Yo" to a cell phone contact. Thanks guys!
